high_descs: Turn right, head towards the door, and then turn right towards the white table.
Pick up the fork on the table.
Turn right and head towards the sink on your right.
Place the fork in the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Turn around and head towards the coffee maker, turn left to face that side.
Open the drawer at the end of the counter and place the fork in it.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean fork in the drawer at the end of the counter.

high_descs: Go right and then right again to face the white table.
Pick the fork up from the table.
Go right and then turn to face the sink.
Put the fork in the sink and turn the water on and then turn it off and pick the fork up.
Turn around and face the drawer on the far left.
Put the fork in the drawer and then shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork in a drawer.

high_descs: Move to the right of the door to the table.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Move to the sink to the left of the fridge.
Place the fork in the sink and run water for a moment before picking up the fork and turning off the water.
Turn around to the counter to the left of the stove.
Open the drawer farthest from the stove and place the fork inside and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork from the table into the drawer farthest to the left from the stove.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the table across the room, then turn to the right to face the table.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Turn to your right and walk to the sink across the room, then turn to the right to face the sink.
Place the fork in the sink to the left of the tomato, turn the water on to wash the fork, turn the water off, then pick the fork back up.
Turn around to the counter behind you and face the drawer on the far left.
Open the drawer on the far left, put the fork near the back of the drawer, and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn around, walk until you reach the door, and turn right to face the table.
Pick up the fork from the front middle of the table.
Turn around, then face the sink to the right.
Wash the fork in the sink.
Turn around to the counter next to the stove.
Open the drawer furthest from the stove and place the fork in it.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed fork in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the table.
Pick up a fork.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Rinse off the fork.
Turn around and open the drawer on the far let.
Put the fork in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed fork in a drawer.
